{"tid":846817,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國對山口組發動經濟制裁","createTime":"2018-10-03T16:42:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T02:38:19.000Z","uid":28765,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9be9eb9f78652035e541d818dd6d48b7e9f7b4f3","tid":846817,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T16:42:21.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕美國宣佈新一起經濟制裁，不過這回不是瞄準國家，而是日本黑道組織山口組。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國財政部周二宣布，將對日本黑道組織山口組旗下的兩間相關公司、以及山口組的4名高層實施經濟制裁，被列入制裁名單中的對象，美國將會凍結其由美國管轄的資產，並且禁止美國人、美國企業和制裁對象有經貿往來。<br />\n<br />\n美國財政部轄下專門負責打擊洗錢及金融犯罪部門的副部長曼德爾科（Sigal Mandelker）表示，日本這些犯罪集團從性交易、走私武器、勒索等非法行為獲利，因此美國要對這些日本犯罪集團施加更多壓力。<br />\n<br />\n曼德爾科同時表示，美國下一步會瞄準和本次制裁目標的合作對象，以破壞犯罪組織在全球的金融體系。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2569584\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2569584&d=Fy5mRzf55vqRWDYzuBMPkhxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=feca0386\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2569584&h=e3419034\" target=\"_blank\">http://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2569584</a><br />\n<br />\n美國呢排好落力打黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"257e00ef86b88c64a55b1bd0646f00410a029374","tid":846817,"uid":34293,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T16:43:43.000Z","msg":"咁共產黨呢？"},{"pid":"b44a6c21b952a5f4c414399ffeed94298fa6fc9b","tid":846817,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T16:43:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18a2e4faa6aba714072b1681a8501e2df79d0e3","tid":846817,"uid":141151,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"257e00ef86b88c64a55b1bd0646f00410a029374","tid":846817,"uid":34293,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"